room_title: Escape room "White Lady's Castle" by Locked A Rochester Escape Room in Rochester (NY)
room_address: 200 Buell Rd suite A-8 Rochester, NY 14624
room_description: In 1904 you and your team of investigators have reopened the Cold Case Of The Disappearance of Margaret Caldwell along the southern shore of Lake Ontario Without a Trace. The Disappearance has struck the town so the local authorities have turned to your highly-skilled team to help solve the case. Your team has been given access to the castle, but you only have 60 minutes to solve the case before your potential suspects slip away for good.
